00:29:31.670 --> 00:29:34.420
But it turns out when you
look at the games that I play,

00:29:34.420 --> 00:29:36.450
that is the type of gamer I am.

00:29:36.450 --> 00:29:40.320
And if I look ahead, I
can compare my profile

00:29:40.320 --> 00:29:41.090
