00:29:41.090 --> 00:29:43.040
And they may be an
action game player

00:29:43.040 --> 00:29:44.670
or they may play a
lot of music games.

00:29:44.670 --> 00:29:47.445
And that gives me an invitation
to talk to my friends

00:29:47.445 --> 00:29:49.540
and something to compare with.

00:29:49.540 --> 00:29:52.040
And as a developer, you can
go to Google Play Developer

00:29:52.040 --> 00:29:52.800
Console today.

00:29:52.800 --> 00:29:56.040
If you have achievements, you
