type of experience.

00:30:05.820 --> 00:30:07.427
I mentioned
comparing to friends,

00:30:07.427 --> 00:30:09.190
so this is my friend Tom.

00:30:09.190 --> 00:30:11.750
And here I can see all
the different games

00:30:11.750 --> 00:30:13.360
that he's played in
different genres.

00:30:13.360 --> 00:30:14.860
And I can kind of
see that oh, he's

00:30:14.860 --> 00:30:17.441
this really cool arcade player.

00:30:17.441 --> 00:30:19.190
And he loves playing
those types of games.

00:30:19.190 --> 00:30:22.720
And that's how he's gotten to
